Download and connect to Dataset 7

Download table Border crossing entry

From this step we are going to create project by following step by step instruction. Before staring project creation, we need to download data.


Click to top left corner red button to download data US Border Crossing Entry.

unzip it and save it into your desired location.

File should be saved as xml format.



Connect to Data set

-        Start new project file

-        Click on Get Data tab

-        Select more, select xml source then connect

-        Select your file location

-        Load it  

 


How to data sources in power BI ? Watch 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8xtCegPe2Y
